      "updated": 1772864721044,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API -> its a request with a perticular path to servers for requesting to\nget/post/delete/update data.\n\nAPI methods -> \n                    1. GET -> to receive data \n                    2. POST -> to send data to server\n                    3. DELETE -> to delete a data\n                    4. PUT -> to update single data \n                    5. PATCH -> to update multiple data\n                 \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API -> its a request with a perticular path to servers for requesting to\nget/post/delete/update data.\n\nAPI methods -> \n                    1. GET -> to receive data \n                    2. POST -> to send data to server\n                    3. DELETE -> to delete a data\n                    4. PUT -> to update single data \n                    5. PATCH -> to update multiple data\n                 \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
